  "detailed_description": "The big 1.5 update is coming in next month!<br>We listened to user feedbacks and working on a lot of changes.<br><br>- We redesign some game mechanics<br>- We improve the gaming experience<br><br>Add the game to your wishlist and wait for the update!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617600/extras/85a6b960e867f83520221c470e555575.avif?t=1626934230\" width=616 height=108 /></span><br><br>Survive Avalon is a sci-fi open world survival game combined with FPS and horror elements.<br><br>The protagonist's spaceship crashes on an unknown planet.<br>You need to explore the planet, hunt for food, and collect resources.<br><br><br>The life is dangerous on Avalon. Every minute is another challenge.<br>Far from your home, you can only count on yourself. <br>Are you ready?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617600/extras/4e92327dbca0a355bb338800ba1b41fb.avif?t=1626934230\" width=616 height=108 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Huge World: There are 3 large forests, a city, snowy mountins and a cave system.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Diversified Opponents: You can meet a variety of opponents. Animals, space creatures and monsters. </ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Item Crafting like ammo and food.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Dungeons: If you want a bigger challenge, visit the Haunted Forest.</ul>",
  "about_the_game": "The big 1.5 update is coming in next month!<br>We listened to user feedbacks and working on a lot of changes.<br><br>- We redesign some game mechanics<br>- We improve the gaming experience<br><br>Add the game to your wishlist and wait for the update!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617600/extras/85a6b960e867f83520221c470e555575.avif?t=1626934230\" width=616 height=108 /></span><br><br>Survive Avalon is a sci-fi open world survival game combined with FPS and horror elements.<br><br>The protagonist's spaceship crashes on an unknown planet.<br>You need to explore the planet, hunt for food, and collect resources.<br><br><br>The life is dangerous on Avalon. Every minute is another challenge.<br>Far from your home, you can only count on yourself. <br>Are you ready?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617600/extras/4e92327dbca0a355bb338800ba1b41fb.avif?t=1626934230\" width=616 height=108 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Huge World: There are 3 large forests, a city, snowy mountins and a cave system.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Diversified Opponents: You can meet a variety of opponents. Animals, space creatures and monsters. </ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Item Crafting like ammo and food.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">* Dungeons: If you want a bigger challenge, visit the Haunted Forest.</ul>",
